ood/happy-birthday-hema-malini-as-original-dream-girl-turns-71-see-her-family-pics-with-dharmendra-esha-deol/story-zLAwJpHkknX7QJWOcUR7xL.html |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=Hindustan Times |date=16 October 2019 |language=en}}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱮᱡ ᱟᱭᱚ ᱟᱨ ᱵᱚᱠᱚᱛ ᱠᱩᱲᱤ ᱥᱟᱶ ᱛᱟᱢᱤᱞ ᱯᱟᱹᱨᱥᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱨᱚᱲ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ <ref>{{cite news |last1=Pradhan |first1=Bharathi S. |title=Esha Deol’s big fat wedding |url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/7-days/esha-deols-big-fat-wedding/cid/407170 |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=www.telegraphindia.com |date=24 June 212 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Syed Firdaus Ashraf |title=I am today's woman: Esha Deol |url=https://www.rediff.com/movies/2004/may/19esha.htm |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=www.rediff.com |date=19 May 2004}}</ref>

